div.p: FIFO select victims based solely on load_time. In Step 05, VPN 0 is accessed (a Hit). In a smart cache (LRU), this would move VPN 0 to the back of the queue. However, in FIFO, the queue position remains unchanged. Result: Even though VPN 0 was used at Step 05, it remains the "Oldest" and is evicted in Step 06 to make room for VPN 3.
